  "text": "[15] The previous section has indicated that 2006 and 2007 were the worst years in terms of fire activity, so it was decided to focus on 2007 as a main study case due to MISR data availability, as well as 2009 to include data from the most recent year. To study the dynamics of the air pollution emissions from their sources, the MISR smoke plume product has been applied [CITATION_1] .",
